social_posts.post_text: Thank you for sunshine, thank you for rain, thank you for joy, thank you for pain 🫶🏻
If it costs you your peace then it’s too expensive
Those who flow how life flows know they need no other force..🧬

If no one told you today
I 💌 you
old keys won’t open new doors
Simple dreams in a complex universe
All this ocean still no frank
Probably somewhere with a flower in my hair
Forget your ego remember your soul
The only constant in life is change
You are here to understand yourself, not to be understood 🫀
when the month was so fun you couldn’t even capture all the good moments on camera 🙈
Time will take us where we need to be
No one is you and that’s your power
Another lap around the sun on this blue full moon🌕🎂❤️
Life is fun when you play it like a game
Attracted to everything attached to nothing
Eyes open, mind open, heart open
I just want to dream with my eyes open
More impressed with the little things
Just being alive is in itself a little thrilling, pleasant, romantic, and miraculous
Call it fate, call it karma
